{"id":672,"type":4,"name":"Quake 4","name_cn":"雷神之锤4","date":"2005-10-18","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/2d/ea/672_3Qq81.jpg","rating":{"rank":3098,"total":38,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":4,"6":5,"7":16,"8":9,"9":3,"10":0},"score":7},"summary":"　　《QUAKE 4》将会是系列中第一款让你扮演真正有名字的主角的游戏。他是一名太空舰队队员，名叫Matthew Kane，是突击队中的精锐，有着神秘的过去。Kane被派遣到Rhino 小队中，这个小组和多个小组一起被派进攻strogg 的故乡——Stroggos行星。实际上，《QUAKE 4》是《QUAKE 2》的后续之作。在《QUAKE 2》中，主人公是一个无名的太空船员，他的任务是击退恶心的strogg，这些strogg为捕捉到的生物装上机械部分来改进他们的身体，然后为他们植入神经控制将他们转变为没有头脑的奴隶。游戏的巅峰战斗发生在Stroggos行星上，主人公来到这个行星，杀掉了stogg的首领“makron”，可惜这个致命的打击并没有结束这场斗争。现在地球派遣了像Rhino 小队这样的太空舰队进攻strogg行星，以永久地解除整个宇宙受到的威胁。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>雷神之锤4</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/32572\">Raven Software</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/17518\">Activision</a>、<a href=\"/person/10310\">Bethesda Softworks</a></li><li><span>协力: </span><a href=\"/person/23616\">id Software</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Quake IV</li><li><span>平台: </span>PC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Linux</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Mac OS X</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Xbox 360</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>FPS</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>id Tech 4</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>单人，多人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2005年10月18日</li><li><span>技术总监: </span>John Carmack</li>","collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":2,"wish":6,"collect":52,"doing":0},"tags":[{"name":"PC","count":6},{"name":"id","count":2},{"name":"主角改造计划","count":2},{"name":"雷神之锤","count":1},{"name":"FPS","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":23616,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8a/8a/23616_prsn_nA7HE.jpg","name":"id Software","desc":"协力"},{"id":17518,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/cb/6c/17518_prsn_bBbhR.jpg","name":"Activision","desc":"发行"},{"id":10310,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5f/1c/10310_prsn_t588m.jpg","name":"Bethesda Softworks","desc":"发行"},{"id":32572,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/de/f0/32572_prsn_EByEB.jpg","name":"Raven Softwa